---
title: Golden Parmesan Halloumi Schnitzels with Cherry Tomato Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! We’ve been looking forward to showing off this one. A sharp cheesy crumb coats tender halloumi to transform it into the ultimate schnitzel. Add a dollop of smokey aioli for a flavourful finish.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/660f935ee0fc814eeb151444-3d2383fa.jpeg
